info.title: XigniteGlobalMetals
info.description: Provide real-time currency foreign exchange information and calculations.

post.description: Get cross sectional historical metal quotes at a given time.
Get intraday bars of specified intervals within a time range.
Get real time extended metal quote.
Get historical metal quote at a given time.
Get historical metal quote by a given time.
Get cross sectional historical metal quotes by a given time.
Get historical metal quotes time series.
Get historical metal quotes based on Legacy London spot prices.
Get intraday tick at given time.
Get intraday ticks of specified intervals within a time range.
Get intraday bar at given time.
Get intraday bars of specified intervals within a time range.
Get last london fixing metal quotes.
Get historical london fixing metal quotes time series.

GetRealTimeMetalQuotesOutput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Body>
  <tns:GetRealTimeMetalQuotesResponse xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/">
   <tns:GetRealTimeMetalQuotesResult>
    <tns:MetalQuote><!-- between zero and unlimited repetitions of this element -->
     <tns:Outcome><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Outcome>
     <tns:Message>string</tns:Message>
     <tns:Identity>string</tns:Identity>
     <tns:Delay><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Delay>
     <tns:Name>string</tns:Name>
     <tns:Symbol>string</tns:Symbol>
     <tns:Unit>string</tns:Unit>
     <tns:QuoteType>string</tns:QuoteType>
     <tns:Currency>string</tns:Currency>
     <tns:Date>string</tns:Date>
     <tns:Time>string</tns:Time>
     <tns:Bid><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Bid>
     <tns:Mid><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Mid>
     <tns:Ask><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Ask>
     <tns:Spread><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Spread>
     <tns:Source>string</tns:Source>
    </tns:MetalQuote>
   </tns:GetRealTimeMetalQuotesResult>
  </tns:GetRealTimeMetalQuotesResponse>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
